{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Privacy <span class="text-primary">Policy</span></h1>
        <p class="text-text-muted">Last updated: March 13, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-icons text-primary">visibility</span>
                1. Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <p>
                We collect information you provide directly to us when creating an account, such as your username, email address, and optional profile details (bio, location, etc.). We also collect data about your activity on the site, including ratings and reviews.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-icons text-primary">storage</span>
                2. How We Use Your Information
            </h2>
            <p>
                Your information is used to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
                <li>Provide and maintain our services.</li>
                <li>Personalize your experience.</li>
                <li>Communicate with you about updates or support.</li>
                <li>Maintain the security and integrity of our platform.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-icons text-primary">share</span>
                3. Information Sharing
            </h2>
            <p>
                We do not sell your personal information. Your public profile data (username, avatar, bio, reviews) is visible to other users unless you set your profile to private in your settings.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-icons text-primary">security</span>
                4. Data Security
            </h2>
            <p>
                We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-icons text-primary">delete_forever</span>
                5. Your Rights
            </h2>
            <p>
                You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time through your account settings. When you delete your account, all your personal data and uploaded files (avatars, banners) are removed from our systems.
            </p>
        </section>

        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5">
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">
                For any privacy-related inquiries, please email privacy@kccatalogue.com.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
